{"id":476,"category_slug":"english-conversations","category_name":"Conversations","position":78,"title":"78. Buying a Present - In a Jeweller's shop","subtitle":"","level":"B1","parts":10,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/english-conversations/78-buying-a-present---in-a-jewellers-shop.476/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/78-buying-a-present---in-a-jewellers-shop-2022-03-07-21-30-03/0-78-buying-a-present---in-a-jewellers-shop.mp3","transcript":"I'm trying to find a wedding anniversary present for my wife.\nYes, sir. What exactly are you looking for?\nI'm not sure, really. Perhaps you can help me.\nRight... I'll show you some pendants.\nNo, I bought a pendant for her birthday.\nMaybe a necklace, then.\nThese necklaces are made of gold.\nYes... I like this one. What's the stone?\nIt's a ruby, sir... and it's only $1200!\nAh... well, perhaps you could show me some bracelets, then.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T20:49:02","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"I'm trying to find a wedding anniversary present for my wife.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/78-buying-a-present---in-a-jewellers-shop-2022-03-07-21-30-03/1.mp3","time_start":4.58,"time_end":7.64},{"position":2,"content":"Yes, sir. What exactly are you looking for?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/78-buying-a-present---in-a-jewellers-shop-2022-03-07-21-30-03/2.mp3","time_start":7.64,"time_end":10.23},{"position":3,"content":"I'm not sure, really. Perhaps you can help me.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/78-buying-a-present---in-a-jewellers-shop-2022-03-07-21-30-03/3.mp3","time_start":10.23,"time_end":12.88},{"position":4,"content":"Right... I'll show you some pendants.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/78-buying-a-present---in-a-jewellers-shop-2022-03-07-21-30-03/4.mp3","time_start":12.88,"time_end":15.17},{"position":5,"content":"No, I bought a pendant for her birthday.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/78-buying-a-present---in-a-jewellers-shop-2022-03-07-21-30-03/5.mp3","time_start":15.26,"time_end":17.56},{"position":6,"content":"Maybe a necklace, then.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/78-buying-a-present---in-a-jewellers-shop-2022-03-07-21-30-03/6.mp3","time_start":17.63,"time_end":19.28},{"position":7,"content":"These necklaces are made of gold.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/78-buying-a-present---in-a-jewellers-shop-2022-03-07-21-30-03/7.mp3","time_start":19.28,"time_end":21.31},{"position":8,"content":"Yes... I like this one. What's the stone?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/78-buying-a-present---in-a-jewellers-shop-2022-03-07-21-30-03/8.mp3","time_start":21.34,"time_end":24.24},{"position":9,"content":"It's a ruby, sir... and it's only $1200!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/78-buying-a-present---in-a-jewellers-shop-2022-03-07-21-30-03/9.mp3","time_start":24.24,"time_end":28.2},{"position":10,"content":"Ah... well, perhaps you could show me some bracelets, then.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/english-conversations/78-buying-a-present---in-a-jewellers-shop-2022-03-07-21-30-03/10.mp3","time_start":28.2,"time_end":31.94}]}